### PRODUCTS
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products

###

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$expand=supplier,category

###

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$filter=stock lt 10

###

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Products?$orderby=price desc

###

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/Customers

###

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/report/ProductCatalog

###

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/report/OrderReport

###

GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/report/LowStockAlert

###

